{
  "text": "Smoker's melanosis e Incorrect. Smoker's melanosis presents with diffuse patches or numerous small melanotic macules in the anterior labial gingiva of the mandible. [CITATION_1] The oral distribution and nail involvement makes smoker's melanosis unlikely.",
